scenes.description: The three Hololive Indonesia members (Kobo, Kaela, Zeta) are on a neon-lit stage. They run in, stop, and discuss their excitement for the concert.
They discuss the title of the concert, 'Chromatic Future', and its meaning regarding their 5th anniversary.
Zeta encourages fans to use the hashtag. They reflect on the shock and significance of a 9-member concert.
They talk about future goals like world domination and thank the sponsors.
They reveal their new 3D idol outfits and pose for the camera.
